  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "EMURGO as a DRep votes YES on Withdraw 1,684,050 ada for Tx3 by TxPipe: Open API Layer for Cardano's dApp Platform, with rationale outlined below.\n\nThis proposal successfully completed the off-chain community governance process on the Hydra voting platform, crossing the required 67% approval threshold. EMURGO respects the legitimacy of this community-led process and votes YES in recognition of the mandate that the Cardano community has clearly expressed. For these reasons, EMURGO votes yes."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}